P_n^{(\alpha, \beta)}(x)=\frac{(-1)^n}{2^nn!}(1-x)^{-\alpha}(1+x)^{-\beta}\frac{d^n}{dx^n}((1-x)^{\alpha}(1+x)^{\beta}(1-x^2)^n)
\sum_{s=0}^n \binom{n+\alpha}{s}\binom{n+\beta}{n-s}(\frac{x-1}{2})^{n-s}(\frac{x+1}{2})^s
